By Mutiat Alli As promised, multi-talented Nigerian-American rapper, King Joel have fulfilled his promise of awarding four mothers who emerged winners during this Mother’s Day giveaway via his Instagram social media handle with a cash prize of N500,000 each and N1M cash recipient. It will be recalled that during the Mother’s Day celebration; Joel has announced that he will rolling out a total cash of N2.5M Naira to celebrate the value of mothers in a child’s upbringing. Despite awarding the winners, Joel disclosed that via his charity organization tagged ‘ Joel LivingGod Foundation’ he would be doing a lot for African women both home and abroad to help them grow their businesses and also give them self development support. He said’ My foundation is solely created to making life better for people living in abject poverty, diseases and affected county across the globe with major focus on Africa at the moment’ On accountability, Joel noted that his team in Nigeria spearheaded by Chiori Daniel Cole ensures that funds are disbursed accordingly at all time and also help in bringing to our notice vulnerable cases that needed utmost attention.